<subSubSection id="9A2EEF325FCD1DF0296F121E4D393E4B" pageId="null" pageNumber="816" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="F8547C7887703FC2DC7983294BFF60CA" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Langstieliges Hornkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="6CB76C6B3D51A378FBD5DCD4CB32126F" pageId="null" pageNumber="816" type="description">
<paragraph id="5EC9545A11619017DAE33507E702CF98" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
Fast keine oder nur sehr lockere Rasen bildend, nur mit einzelnen sterilen Trieben. 
<normalizedToken id="33251EE994AD3C95626106C20C8054DC" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
meist unter der Mitte am breitesten, 
<normalizedToken id="E4DAF1B024E25AF73F1A35A9E532E18B" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">+/-</normalizedToken>
spitz, 0,5-2,9 cm lang. Haare an den 
<normalizedToken id="9BFC2F4B686DD27A488997B2C6239986" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
und am Kelch 0,3-0,5 mm lang. Oberste 
<normalizedToken id="94B0BAC23B609D713B4055EEEC635442" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
im 
<normalizedToken id="25099B68DAA8E3CBD20ED3B571FA4F01" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
meist oberseits behaart, mit krautiger Spitze. 
<normalizedToken id="536F2294903BD77AE040B1B66FBA289F" originalValue="Kelchblätteri" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Kelchblaetteri</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="3A7CBED300508C274E7CF0A63180457A" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">+/-</normalizedToken>
spitz. 
<emphasis id="6A66BA7C7CBEFFE1C3022D9ABBBC3A46" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
<normalizedToken id="937C3DBF711ACEC44D60704D226624F4" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
7-10 mm lang, 1-1
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="08400E9A0F3397C1A4DE09C45AA9EAD7" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="1128B34BE0FCECFE6831902E41F52BC9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="9F18CE31CA0BC67C543C1AE88E3159F2" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Samen 1-1,5 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="A50CC42A503BD1F996EA7FF43C51CE6E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="449300E6B814A73C3A6A7A68DB7BE2FF" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
<emphasis id="041076B89F0EDC3F245A4F85C486117C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="78E049E442CA30EE4BA7BE94E67ED9B7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">36:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Wallis und vom 
<normalizedToken id="2AD6F16E91D88E60972DC5B3526FB6FD" originalValue="Sustenpaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Sustenpass</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="F9B379E577B561CC4E630C1819B2BE74" originalValue="Söllner" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Soellner</normalizedToken>
1954).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F88B00BB92F4EF9E249E909D636E97F9" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
<emphasis id="8632F118A9E49766AEAD9180D712633F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin, selten subalpin (herabgeschwemmt). Steinige, feuchte, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="6532053FBF11A59681E780A99AF8C34F" originalValue="Schüttböden" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Schuettboeden</normalizedToken>
. Felsschutt, 
<normalizedToken id="B8D891F39C723C3052DE3DEF2F72BAB0" originalValue="Moränen" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Moraenen</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="185D2B71092A0FF22961BF265FF63ACE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Oxyrietum digynae</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="5C4645EAA32833922671C3F05D2A497D" originalValue="Lüdi" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Luedi</normalizedToken>
) Br.-Bl. 1926.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="655E0D9F830DEF1968583195D3FC678D" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">
<emphasis id="E01154FC662AAD7C5010396E7F1673E2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Verbreitung. Alpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Alpen (von den Kottischen Alpen bis zu den Hohen Tauern). - Im Gebiet: Zentral-und 
<normalizedToken id="F1E8215917755EEACA937A8F414F9E8D" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
, nicht 
<normalizedToken id="D27D113A35C24A8647D9E5D050E91FBE" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">haeufig</normalizedToken>
; Nordalpen (Grimsel, Susten, Glarus, St. Galler Oberland, St. 
<normalizedToken id="8C28914042BA2E76B89049575CC34EA2" originalValue="Anthönierjoch" pageId="null" pageNumber="816">Anthoenierjoch</normalizedToken>
), selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
